window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I'm a city boy, not a cowboy. I'm way out of my league on a horse ranch in Texas.</p> <p>Falling for the sexy horse vet was never my intention. Especially when I find out she could be dating a killer.</p> <p>Sneaking around with her? Not my brightest idea, but someone's got to protect her.</p> <p>It's just one summer. One casual fling.</p> <p>Until it becomes everything but.</p> <p>This book can be listened to as a stand-alone novel.</p> <p>If you fell in love with the Mitchell sisters, you won't want to miss this next-generation series. It's sexy, sweet, and suspenseful all rolled into one.</p>"; 
